data.description: Beautiful condo, laminate wood flooring throughout (extra planks in garage), triple pane patio door with built in mini blinds, Beautiful kitchen with granite countertops, galley style with wood/glass front cabinets and stainless steel appliances. Pass through counter to living room. Two spacious bedrooms, Lots of natural light. Private paver patio. Two car attached garage with opener. Washer & dryer stay. This home has a water softener & furnace is newer, 2018, AC unit new last year.   This is a relocation, please allow extra time for responses. See agent remarks, there is an attachment that has to be submitted with all offers.
